Significant events and approaches for the overall study following participant enrollment, but prior to group assignment Pre-Assignment Details Enrollment took place at five Network centers and their associated satellite facilities between July 8, 2008 and February 28, 2011. The main centers are located in Ohio, Texas, Florida, Minnesota, and Tennessee. Study brochures, patient informational DVDs, and clinical trials.gov were among the tools used for recruitment.
